{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/init"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"}],"role":"symbol","title":"init","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(im)init","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/init","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:*Qo","text":"id","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Version: 8.0.1"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk","type":"topic","title":"ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","abstract":[{"text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/init":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/init","title":"init","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/init"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"value":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/title"},{"value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/fragments"},{"value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/navigatorTitle"}]}]}